name: ColorfulCocktail
description:
By downloading, you agree to the CreativeML Open RAIL-M

This is an all-around model for anime to semi-realistic.

Pros:

  • Great results with few words

  • Multiple subjects

  • Intense bright colors

  • Favors symmetry

  • Can use Danbooru tags, long sentences, or both

  • Works well with embeddings and hypernetworks

Cons:

  • No photorealism

  • Poses can be tricky to summon correctly

  • Long heavily emphasized prompts are penalized

  • Sexual acts almost always lead to a Cronenberg fever dream

Tips:

  • To get intense colors, use (monochrome) in the negativ with psychedelic in the positiv

  • Highly recommending playing around with clip skip

VAE used : AnythingV3

By downloading, you agree to any licenses listed below.

Models used:

  • Anything-v3.0

  • EimisAnimeDiffusion_1.0v

  • ACertainModel

  • F222_v1

  • Dreamlike-diffusion-1.0 (license)
